Support system (brief)
What it is

Public site + admin inbox for SEOI support tickets
Live: https://support.seoi.in
Code: ~/shopify-apps/aiseo_support → GitHub legal.git
Server folder: ~/support_aiseo
DB: same Postgres as Shopify app — ai_product_desc
URLs

/privacy-policy — public privacy text
/faq — public FAQ
/help — public “Support (Shopify App)” text
/support — admin Support inbox (login required)
Shopify admin inbox (optional): https://support.seoi.in/admin → proxies to ai_seo on port 3000
Apps in inbox

Product Image SEO Optimizer (seoi)
Pay Sync (pay-sync)
Merchants submit tickets from the Shopify app → SupportMessage (tagged to SEOI)
Login

Email/password = AdminUser in DB (same as ADMIN_EMAIL / ADMIN_PASSWORD in ~/ai_seo/.env)
Cookie session via legal-api
Server pieces

Nginx support.seoi.in
Static: /var/www/support-seoi ← copy from ~/support_aiseo/dist
/api/ → 127.0.0.1:4000 (legal-api)
/admin/ → 127.0.0.1:3000 (shopify-app-ai_seo)
PM2
legal-api — Express API (~/support_aiseo/server/index.js)
shopify-app-ai_seo — main Shopify app
Deploy support site

cd ~/support_aiseo
git pull
# ensure .env has DATABASE_URL=...ai_product_desc...
npm install
npm run db:seed          # policy_pages only
npm run build
cp -a dist/. /var/www/support-seoi/
pm2 restart legal-api --update-env
systemctl reload nginx
Deploy DB tables (apps / messages)

cd ~/ai_seo
npx prisma migrate deploy   # SupportApp, SupportMessage, AdminUser, etc.
pm2 restart shopify-app-ai_seo --update-env
Local

cd ~/shopify-apps/aiseo_support
npm run dev                 # Vite :5173 + API :4000
# open http://localhost:5173/support
Important

support_aiseo ≠ Prisma — use npm run db:seed there
Prisma migrations only in ai_seo
After frontend changes, always copy dist → /var/www/support-seoi (Nginx does not use ~/support_aiseo/dist directly)
Don’t commit .env or notepad with passwords


Option B — keep /var/www/support-seoi, always copy after build

Save this as ~/support_aiseo/deploy.sh:

#!/bin/bash
set -e
cd ~/support_aiseo
git pull
npm install
npm run build
rm -rf /var/www/support-seoi/*
cp -a dist/. /var/www/support-seoi/
mkdir -p /var/www/support-seoi/promo
cp -a public/promo/. /var/www/support-seoi/promo/
cp -a public/robots.txt public/sitemap.xml /var/www/support-seoi/
pm2 restart legal-api --update-env
systemctl reload nginx
echo "Deployed."
chmod +x ~/support_aiseo/deploy.sh